{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/key_feutures_steam_short1.png?t=1737660614\" />Forge the destiny of a galaxy on the brink of destruction. As the commander of an ancient AI, your mission is clear: save the galaxy at all costs. Harness the power of advanced industry and epic armies in <strong>Warfactory</strong>, satisfying fusion of Sci-Fi RTS and industrial automation genres. Design, Build and Command your ultimate war machine against an unrelenting alien threat.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/1.gif?t=1737660614\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/key_feutures_steam_short2.png?t=1737660614\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Construct high-tech military production chains to craft everything your army needs \u2014 plasma swords, rocket launchers, massive mech hulls, and more. Every planet is a new challenge, with hostile environments, limited resources, and relentless enemy raids giving a test even for the most efficient war factories.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/2.gif?t=1737660614\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/key_feutures_steam_short3.png?t=1737660614\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You don\u2019t just command armies: you design &amp; assemble every unit from the ground up: producing and transporting hulls, weapons, propulsion systems, and battle programs. Adapt to ever-changing threats and environments with custom strategies. Command massive armies composed of hundreds of unique units combinations.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/3.gif?t=1737660614\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/key_feutures_steam_short4.png?t=1737660614\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into hand-crafted single-player campaign or push your limits in the procedurally generated rogue-lite mode. Discover uncharted planets, unlock gamechanging technology, and upgrade your mothership to face the galaxy-spanning war and win. Will you break the endless cycle of war, or will the galaxy succumb to chaos?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/4.gif?t=1737660614\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737660614","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737660614","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/b51f7defd7ab477b7f0b58a82622ccb69c55bc2e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737660614","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/b51f7defd7ab477b7f0b58a82622ccb69c55bc2e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737660614","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3396160/extras/key_feutures_steam_short1.png?t=1737660614\" />Forge the destiny of a galaxy on the brink of destruction. As the commander of an ancient AI, your mission is clear: save the galaxy at all costs. Harness the power of advan